title: 91: The Dining Out Q&A Episode
itunes:title: The Dining Out Q&A Episode
description: Hungry Girl is here to answer your dining out dilemmas: what words to look for on the menu... how to not overeat at a buffet… and more! Plus, Lisa has the 411 on the healthiest salad toppings and which ones to avoid! So before you go out to dinner tonight, listen closely, take notes, and for even more tips, head on over to our Foodcast page!
itunes:summary: Dining out doesn’t have to be a challenge. Hungry Girl is answering your dining out questions, this week on Chew the Right Thing!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
